2055
01:29:17.955 --> 01:29:19.205
When exploitation

2056
01:29:19.345 --> 01:29:22.485
and trafficking occur within those relationships of trust

2057
01:29:22.865 --> 01:29:26.925
and dependency, the power imbalance is absolute.

